OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784315922
OL,3,CProperties evacuated following
OL,4,Csecurity alert
OL,6,FPolice are at the scene of a security
OL,7,Falert in north Belfast following the
OL,8,Fsearch of a property in the Rosapenna
OL,9,FParade area during the early hours of
OL,10,FFriday morning.
OL,12,FAs part of the operation, properties
OL,13,Fin the surrounding area are being
OL,14,Fevacuated, and the Ardoyne Community
OL,15,FCentre has been opened to provide
OL,16,Fassistance for affected residents.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
