OL,3,CProperties evacuated following
OL,4,Csecurity alert
OL,6,FPolice have established cordons around
OL,7,FRosapenna Street and sections of the
OL,8,FCliftonville Road, urging members of
OL,9,Fthe public to avoid the area until
OL,10,Ffurther notice.
OL,12,FMotorists have also been warned to
OL,13,Fexpect significant traffic disruption
OL,14,Fthroughout the morning, particularly
OL,15,Falong Cliftonville Road, and are
OL,16,Fadvised to use alternative routes
OL,17,Fwhere possible.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
