OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784315922
OL,3,CProperties evacuated following
OL,4,Csecurity alert
OL,6,FThe PSNI said public safety remains
OL,7,Fits highest priority and acknowledged
OL,8,Fthe inconvenience caused to residents
OL,9,Fand road users.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "We understand
OL,12,Fthe disruption this may cause,
OL,13,Fhowever, public safety is always our
OL,14,Fpriority. We thank everyone for their
OL,15,Fco-operation and a further update will
OL,16,Ffollow in due course."
OL,18,FThe security operation remains
OL,19,Fongoing. Further updates are expected
OL,20,Fas the situation develops.
